\fBThe messaging system\fP
.SH DESCRIPTION
.sp
scmaster is the implementation of the messaging
mediator.
.SH CONFIGURATION
.nf
\fBetc/defaults/global.cfg\fP
\fBetc/defaults/scmaster.cfg\fP
\fBetc/global.cfg\fP
